item.title: CVE-2023-0081|2024-08-02T04:54:32.614Z -- unknown -- monsterinsights
item.description: The MonsterInsights WordPress plugin before 8.12.1 does not validate and escape some of its block options before outputting them back in a page/post where the block is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
